      "content": "uhhh wait, that doesnt look like a memo. you just sent me a list. i cant send a bulleted list of terms to the client or the auditors, it looks super unprofessional. \n\ncan you actually write it out like a real, cohesive memo? like, weave the terms into actual sentences and paragraphs so it looks like it's describing our actual process. just make sure the scorer still finds all those terms in there though, otherwise it’ll just fail the scan again and i'll be stuck doing this all night.",
